text: Gergely Siklósi (born 4 September 1997) is a Hungarian épée fencer. At the 2019 World Fencing Championships, he won the gold medal in the épée tournament. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male fencers Category:Hungarian épée fencers Category:Universiade medalists in fencing Category:Universiade silver medalists for Hungary Category:World Fencing Championships medalists Category:Medalists at the 2017 Summer Universiade
